    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>Calendar.getInstance().getActualMaximum(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This returns actual maximum for current month. For example it is February of leap year now, so it returns 29 as <code>int</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 160802,
      "reputation" : 94,
      "user_id" : 381127,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/d534c79c7082a94071d9f15f8b9cd630?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Bruno",
