      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "You should set (DAY_OF_MONTH, 1) first. If you are on 31th of January and set month to February it will skip to March, because the 31th of February does not exist.  <code>Calendar cal = DateUtils.getCalendar(2021, 1, 31); &#47;&#47; DateUtils is custom. cal.set(Calendar.MONTH, Calendar.FEBRUARY); System.out.println(cal.getTime());</code>  &gt;&gt;&gt; Wed Mar 03 00:00:00 CET 2021 @mike"
