    "body" : "<p>Kotlin date extension implementation using <code>java.util.Calendar</code> </p>\n\n<pre><code>fun Date.toEndOfMonth(): Date {\n    return Calendar.getInstance().apply {\n        time = this@toEndOfMonth\n    }.toEndOfMonth().time\n}\n\nfun Calendar.toEndOfMonth(): Calendar {\n    set(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH, getActualMaximum(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH))\n    return this\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can call <code>toEndOfMonth</code> function on each Date object like <code>Date().toEndOfMonth()</code></p>\n"
