    "body" : "<h2><code>java.time.YearMonth</code></h2>\n<p>You can also use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/25/docs/api/java.base/java/time/YearMonth.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>YearMonth</code></a> class with its <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/25/docs/api/java.base/java/time/YearMonth.html#atEndOfMonth()\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>atEndOfMonth</code></a> method.</p>\n<p>Like:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>YearMonth.of(2019,7).atEndOfMonth()  // July 31, 2019.\nYearMonth.of(2019,7).atDay(1)        // July 1, 2019. \n</code></pre>\n<p>See\n<a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/time/YearMonth.html#atEndOfMonth--\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/time/YearMonth.html#atEndOfMonth--</a></p>\n"
